20 Best Torrent Sites January 2026 (Working & Tested)

January 2, 2026 / Torrent

The following guide lists the Best Torrent Sites that are still working and safe to use in 2026.

Finding a reliable torrent site thats safe to use is getting more difficult by the day. With takedowns, fake websites, ISP blocks, privacy concerns, etc. finding a reliable torrenting option can feel like a full-time job.

Even with these hurdles, torrenting still remains popular with over 28 million users participating in P2P file sharing every day.

Our team at TROYPOINT has done the hard work for you by compiling the top torrenting options for movies, TV shows, music, games, ebooks, software, photos, applications, and more.

If you are new to this technology, think of a torrent site like a digital library index. It doesnt host files directly but points you to the users who do.

Torrenting works by grabbing pieces of a file from multiple sources at once, which makes downloads faster and more efficient than pulling from a single server.

Our reviews team at TROYPOINT has ranked the best torrent sites below based on content, safety, categories, user-interface, ad frequency, VPN compatibility, speed, popularity, and user feedback from forums like Reddit.

Be sure to bookmark this page and check back on a regular basis for new torrent submissions provided by users in the TROYPOINT Insider.

    Best Torrent Sites in 2026

    TROYPOINT Tip: Even the most popular torrent sites carry security risks. Popups, fake downloads, and viruses are common. If youre not using a torrent-friendly VPN and Antivirus software youre asking for trouble.

    1. The Pirate Bay

    The Pirate Bay is still one of the most visited torrent sites (and websites) used worldwide. It offers everything from movies and TV shows to games, music, and software.

    Over the years it has undergone legal scrutiny, blocking, and Google Deindexing, yet it continues to thrive as the best torrrent site available today for new users and seasoned visitors as well.

    Its long-standing user base and magnet link support help keep downloads active, even for older files. Look for the green skull icon next to uploaders for verified content.

    Unlike other popular options, the official site for The Pirate Bay has a perfectly clean interface that makes browsing a breeze.

    If you use the Stremio application, you can even install a Pirate Bay Stremio Addon to access these files within the Stremio App. Definitely worth checking out!

    Official Website: thepiratebay.org
    Best For: User-Friendly Interface & Massive Content Library
    VirusTotal Scan: Clean (scan results)

    2. Internet Archive

    The Internet Archive stands as one of the largest non-profit digital libraries on the internet, founded in 1996 with the mission of providing universal access to all knowledge.

    This massive repository offers everything from classic films and shows to historical documents and rare audio recordings. The platform requires no registration and provides completely free access to millions of items.

    Users can search through the archive to find relevant software (such as Kodi and other APKs), view their favorite videos from the past, and download photos/logos all in just a few clicks. This is an underrated website that all torrentors should take advantage of.

    Official Website: archive.org
    Best For: Classic Movies, Vintage Software, Historical Documents
    VirusTotal Scan: Clean (scan results)

    3. 1337x

    1337x remains a top torrent source thanks to its wide library and dedicated uploader base. The site features updated categories across movies, shows, anime, software, and games.

    Its home page layout makes it easy to find trending content with reliable seeders. The search filters help weed out low-quality/fake uploads and you can even browse trending categories and more.

    Make sure to take advantage of the Uploader category that shows who uploads the file so you can see if it is from a verified provider.

    If you want a more personalized experience, create a free account with an anonymous email and get access to more direct links and advanced features. (You can also donate to this torrent website via cryptocurrency if you enjoy the platform.)

    • Official Website: 1337x.to
    • Best For: Large Content Library
    • VirusTotal Scan: One Malicious File (scan results)

    4. Public Domain Torrents

    Public Domain Torrents specializes in classic movies that are no longer protected by copyright law, making them completely free and legal to download and share.

    The site focuses on older films, B-movies, and historical footage that has entered the public domain. Youll find everything from classic Hollywood films to educational documentaries and vintage cartoons that you can download without any legal concerns.

    Downloads are always available for free but if you want to comment/rate titles, make sure to register for an account that provides added benefits.

    Official Website: publicdomaintorrents.info
    Best For: Classic Movies, Historical Films, Educational Content
    VirusTotal Scan: One Suspicious File (scan results)

    5. YTS

    YTS is built around HD movie torrents with smaller file sizes for quick downloads. It pulls millions of visitors monthly due to its consistent release schedule and subtitle support.

    Each title page shows IMDb ratings, trailers, and format details. While the simplicity of the home screen is what draws users to this torrent site, many also disapprove of the heavy popups. (These can be reduced with CleanWeb).

    It is important to note that YTS also only hosts moviesno shows, games, or music, so if you are looking for these you may want to consider an alternative.

    • Official Website: yts.mx
    • Best For: HD Movie Downloads
    • VirusTotal Scan: One Suspicious File (scan results)

    6. Project Gutenberg

    Project Gutenberg holds the distinction of being the oldest digital library, founded in 1971 and offering over 75,000 free eBooks. The collection focuses on works in the public domain, particularly classic literature, poetry, and historical documents.

    The simple interface makes it perfect for students, teachers, and anyone looking to explore classic literature without spending money on expensive textbooks. Best of all, there is absolutely no ads on the site so browsing is as simple as it gets.

    If you are in the market for eBooks, look no further than Project Gutenberg.

    Official Website: gutenberg.org
    Best For: Classic Literature, Poetry, Historical Documents
    VirusTotal Scan: Clean (scan results)

    7. EZTV

    EZTV is known for offering individual TV show episodes with consistent updates across genres. Its one of the oldest brands in the torrent space, though now operated under new ownership.

    The interface is dated, but search tools still work well for locating recent airings. Full seasons on this site are rare, but you can expect episode-by-episode downloads which can be accessed with their daily calendar.

    One major benefit that users can take advantage of is EZTVs customer support options which include a direct email to send ideas, report bugs, and ask questions. If you need further assitance, check out the built-in Forum to request titles, talk to other torrent fans, and learn more about this software!

    • Official Website: eztvx.to
    • Best For: TV Show Episodes
    • VirusTotal Scan: Two Suspicious Files (scan results)

    8. Academic Torrents

    Academic Torrents serves the scientific community by using BitTorrent protocol to share massive research datasets and academic papers. Built by researchers for researchers, this platform addresses the high costs of scientific journals and data storage.

    This legitimate, non-profit platform offers enormous value to researchers, data scientists, and students who need access to academic resources.

    You can search for papers, authors, courses, and more within the websites huge library that considers itself a community maintained repository that functions at a high level!

    Official Website: academictorrents.com
    Best For: Research Datasets, Academic Papers, Scientific Data
    VirusTotal Scan: One Suspicious File (scan results)

    9. LimeTorrents

    LimeTorrents hosts a large public library of torrents ranging from software and anime to films and games. This torrent site includes health indicators so users can pick the safest downloads without worry.

    Its Verified tags and cloud-based search options improve accuracy and the homepage updates frequently with newly added torrents. Make sure to use an adblocker or similar tool to help reduce the ads which are extensive.

    Many will remember LimeWire which was a popular file sharing torrent site for music and LimeTorrents is an extension of this but for much more. Enjoy!

    • Official Website: limetorrents.lol
    • Best For: Beginner-Friendly Experience
    • VirusTotal Scan: One Malicious File (scan results)

    10. Etree

    Etree (electronic tree) has been a cornerstone of the live music community since 1998, dedicated to preserving and sharing high-quality recordings of live concerts.

    The platform focuses on fan-recorded shows that bands have permitted for free distribution. This helps preserve unique live performances while making them accessible to fans worldwide.

    Official Website: etree.org
    Best For: Live Concert Recordings, Bootleg Audio, Music Archives
    VirusTotal Scan: Clean (scan results)

    11. NYAA

    NYAA is the top site for anime torrents, with a dedicated user base uploading both raw and subbed episodes. Its well-organized and regularly updated with Japanese and Korean content.

    Users will especially enjoy navigating through the provided content without interruption as there are no ads! This is something you wont find in most popular torrent sites.

    Torrent health is typically strong, especially for newer or popular titles. Manga, soundtracks, and doujinshi are also available in bulk for efficient downloading.

    • Official Website: nyaa.si
    • Best For: Anime and Manga Content
    • VirusTotal Scan: Clean (scan results)

    12. FitGirl Repacks

    FitGirl Repacks specializes in high-compression PC game torrents that save time and bandwidth. Games are often bundled with pre-crack installers for easier setup and installation on your computer.

    This site is not a traditional index but hosts only the repacks created by FitGirl. You can easily browse through popular repacks (top monthly/yearly) as well as the entire list categorized A-Z.

    In late 2025, German users were unable to access FitGirl Repacks due to blocking order by ISPs without a court order so if you are having problems you may need to speak with your Internet Service Provider.

    Always double-check the domain name as many fake copies and scam sites exist.

    • Official Website: fitgirl-repacks.site
    • Best For: Compressed PC Games
    • VirusTotal Scan: One Suspicious File (scan results)

    13. RuTracker

    RuTracker is one of the largest Russian torrent trackers and hosts a massive collection of files, including music, movies, software, books, and more.

    While the site is mostly in Russian, many English-speaking users rely on browser translation tools to access its valuable content.

    Its especially popular for rare or hard-to-find media, including full discographies and high-quality music files. Registration is required to download torrents, but the process is quick and free.

    • Official Website: rutracker.org
    • Best For: Music and Audio Content
    • VirusTotal Scan: One suspicious file (scan results)

    14. IPTorrents (Private)

    IPTorrents is a private tracker with fast speeds, verified content, and zero ads. Users need an invite or donation to register (difficult to obtain) but once inside, the experience is premium.

    Its library includes media, software, and hard-to-find files in high-quality formats. Uploading and seeding are required to maintain your account.

    If you have questions or concerns, use the support email or join the live irc support channel (no invites provided) and find everything youre looking for.

    • Official Website: iptorrents.com
    • Best For: Private Tracker Experience
    • VirusTotal Scan: One Malicious File (scan results)

    15. Skidrow & Reloaded

    Skidrow & Reloaded focuses on cracked PC game releases and has been around for years. Its structured more like a blog than a torrent index, but magnet links are usually provided.

    Unlike FitGirl Repacks listed above, Skidrow accepts requests so if you are looking for a specific game/repack, simply ask and you shall receive!

    Most files are externally hosted, so caution is needed when clicking download buttons. Comments are limited, so verify file info before launching torrents.

    Please note that there are three malicious files associated with this torrent site so make sure you are protecting yourself with a trusted VPN source.

    • Official Website: skidrowreloaded.com
    • Best For: Cracked Game Releases
    • VirusTotal Scan: Three Malicious Files (scan results)

    16. Torlock

    Torlock brands itself as a No Fakes torrent site and rewards users for flagging fake uploads. It features a wide range of content including anime, software, and eBooks.

    The best way to find media you are looking for is by browsing the provided categories that vary by year and even include past sporting events such as MMA and more.

    Despite aggressive pop-ups, its torrent verification rate is higher than average. Its best to stick to homepage categories as search results can bring spammy links.

    • Official Website: torlock-official.live
    • Best For: Verified Content Only
    • VirusTotal Scan: One Malicious File (scan results)

    17. IGGGAMES

    IGG-Games delivers cracked games across various genres with simplified install guides. The site attracts heavy traffic and includes direct downloads along with torrents.

    The biggest downfall is the popups and ads that will riddle your screen but it seems as though this does not bother many as it is still one of the most popular torrent games sites available today.

    Most titles are tested by the uploader community and come with setup walkthroughs. Beware that this website is frequently cloned, stick with the .com domain only.

    • Official Website: igg-games.com
    • Best For: Game Downloads with Guides
    • VirusTotal Scan: One Suspicious File (scan results)

    18. TorrentDownloads

    TorrentDownloads has been around for years and is a reliable choice for finding movies, TV shows, games, software, and books.

    The interface may feel dated, but the massive database and advanced filtering tools make it easy to locate quality torrents. Its especially useful for older or obscure files that arent as available on newer torrent platforms.

    Be prepared for a few aggressive ads, as using a VPN and ad blocker is highly recommended.

    • Official Website: torrentdownloads.pro
    • Best For: Older and Rare Content
    • VirusTotal Scan: One Suspicious File (scan results)

    19. Torrentz

    Originally launched in 2003, Torrentz has been one of the best, most popular torrent sites for over 20 years and is still thriving to this day.

    With meta-search capabilities that aggregates and compiles results from numerous sources, you are sure to have a plethora of magnets and links to select from.

    Users oftentimes comment and provide feedback on provided torrents so you know what you are getting before you begin the download process.

    • Official Website: torrentz.eu.com
    • Best For: Meta-Search Capabilities
    • VirusTotal Scan: No Suspicious Files (scan results)

    20. AniDex

    AniDex focuses on anime torrents but also includes manga, light novels, soundtracks, and some Western content.

    The site supports both English-subbed and raw versions, catering to a wide range of anime fans. Its clean layout and user-tagged uploads help visitors easily find what theyre looking for.

    AniDex is community-driven and known for strong seed health and detailed upload notes.

    • Official Website: anidex.info
    • Best For: Anime Community Features
    • VirusTotal Scan: One Suspicious File (scan results)

    Are Torrent Sites Legal?

    Torrent websites themselves are legal because they use the BitTorrent protocol to share files, which is a legitimate technology.

    However, the legality of the content shared on these platforms depends on copyright laws in your country. Countries like Greece will imprison & fine torrent users.

    In the United States, torrenting itself is legal but sharing copyrighted content is illegal and could potentially lead to fines or prosecution.

    This includes copyrighted videos, music, software, etc. If youre caught and found guilty, penalties include up to $250K in fines and up to five years in prison.

    The two laws in the US that directly affect torrenting and P2P activity are the Digital Millennium Copyright Act (DMCA) and the No Electronic Theft Act (NET Act).

    And keep in mind that America ISPs are monitoring and storing user download data for months or even years. AT&T for instance stores this data for a year while Comcast stores it for at least six months.

    We are not attorneys at TROYPOINT so you should always do your own research and ensure you are only accessing content from the public domain thats not protected by copyright.
